   EN: Deliberately NO 'display: block' rule here -- this scene exists specifically to
       prove the UA-stylesheet works; it must rely SOLELY on glintfx's embedded default.
   PT: Deliberadamente SEM regra 'display: block' aqui -- esta cena existe para provar
       a UA-stylesheet; deve depender SOMENTE do default embutido do glintfx. */
body { background-color: #101010; }
.red  { width: 100px; height: 40px; background-color: #ff0000; }
.blue { width: 100px; height: 40px; background-color: #0000ff; }
